<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="14Dec1932"><font color="red">14 December 1932</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver from Paul L&eacute;on): Mr Joyce &hellip; is alone in his opinion that his daughter should be kept home &hellip; last week he had two lachrymose collapses &hellip; He had two simultaneous offers for the deluxe publication of the new fragment from Transition </div>
